{"tid":703101,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭欣宜重提18歲時向吳卓羲收過百投訴　自覺處理得好：我冇在意過","createTime":"2018-06-15T12:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T10:21:14.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"a4e00bf8ad22aa463bf52979c4a4614aa431365c","tid":703101,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"鄭欣宜（Joyce）近日接受奇妙電視節目《天下第一friend 2》主持鄭紹康（Francis）訪問。提到Joyce自小在眾人目光焦點下成長，她坦言當初未有想過幕前工作：「我小時候喜歡表演，娛樂別人令我很有滿足感。但我在大學選科時，其實選擇電影製作，打算從事幕後工作。」<br />\n<br />\nJoyce更親述當年以白雪公主造型演出向吳卓羲獻吻，Francis指當時收到過百宗投訴，對於當時只得18歲的Joyce是否受打擊。Joyce表示：「自己當時是不懂得面對，現在回想覺得都處理得很好。我都無在意件事，我只是依照劇本演出，也沒有收取酬勞。第一次演出來說算不錯，是有點生硬，但唱得還可以。」Joyce更安慰出於保護自己而激動回應的父母，Joyce雖對事件無在意，但介意之後其他人對自己存在攻擊性。幸而入行前有此經歷，Joyce謂今日不會因同類事情受傷。<br />\n<br />\n提到上年年尾Joyce跌斷腳，要做手術，陳淑芬當時照料在旁，Joyce回想起亦為此感動落淚。Joyce淚盈滿眶的向Francis表示，當時未有告之父親，自己一個面對其實很害怕，感激陳淑芬一直相伴，又為她下廚煲湯細心照料。Joyce謂：「陳太好清楚我性格，從來願意讓我自己闖蕩，沒有說過要簽我或去管束我，對我是無私的愛。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/204042_8922f7802d10bdce5f1543a7001545c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F204042_8922f7802d10bdce5f1543a7001545c6.png&h=481a48e6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/15/204044_8922f7802d10bdce5f1543a7001545c6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F15%2F204044_8922f7802d10bdce5f1543a7001545c6.png&h=55f821e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/199509/鄭欣宜重提18歲時向吳卓羲收過百投訴-自覺處理得好-我冇在意過\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F199509%2F%E9%84%AD%E6%AC%A3%E5%AE%9C%E9%87%8D%E6%8F%9018%E6%AD%B2%E6%99%82%E5%90%91%E5%90%B3%E5%8D%93%E7%BE%B2%E6%94%B6%E9%81%8E%E7%99%BE%E6%8A%95%E8%A8%B4-%E8%87%AA%E8%A6%BA%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%BE%97%E5%A5%BD-%E6%88%91%E5%86%87%E5%9C%A8%E6%84%8F%E9%81%8E&d=zKocEFSy1qa9rbVPg05ZiQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5aa9df4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/199509/鄭欣宜重提18歲時向吳卓羲收過百投訴-自覺處理得好-我冇在意過</a>"},{"pid":"5b2b558caaeff68f1ed99349c0b7df40e7871b1c","tid":703101,"uid":82917,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:43:16.000Z","msg":"白雪 白雪呢個名真係好難聽 好難聽呀！"},{"pid":"634b54eafa9d047c2b3971d47321e91da8e98360","tid":703101,"uid":69794,"like":18,"dislike":1,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:44:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.scampp.com/holding Wilbur on his 3rd BD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.scampp.com%2Fholding%20Wilbur%20on%20his%203rd%20BD.jpg&h=311d75f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c7404f93040178d1d8eeea3c8ffa8080e98e1f0d","tid":703101,"uid":67346,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:46:49.000Z","msg":"但對吳卓羲嚟講就變咗一生人嘅陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n件肥婆真係冇諗過人地感受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270e84499c55055dcf5ee91617231e112b48c01d","tid":703101,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:48:12.000Z","msg":"收啦"},{"pid":"88e21dd9270672a6feff35eaf4ad878b523b591e","tid":703101,"uid":29336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5021f3900a4f48b2801aea66a19031d1cb57c498","tid":703101,"uid":1779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:50:18.000Z","msg":"過主啦屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5856f1aa5c4a2662cea98b90d7e81124c69674","tid":703101,"uid":69794,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T12:50:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06